larson eric <elarson@ux1.cso.uiuc.edu> wrote:
>The makers of MathCad put it best by deciding to eschew an OS/2 version and
>simply develop for Win32s.  I believe the lionshare of small development
>houses will do likely.  It's only the big houses that will try both OS/2
